    {
      "id": "29-autonomic-reflexes",
      "number": 29,
      "title": "Autonomic Reflexes",
      "layout": "right",
      "reveal": "right",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "content": "The ANS uses reflexes to maintain homeostasis."
        },
